Over 1.2 year of practical experience in hadoop, I have gained knowledge on Bigdata as a developer and also in the field of administration and configuration of its few ecosystem components. While working on hadoop, I have got experience in the following components: Map Reduce, Pig, Hive, Hbase, Oozie and Sqoop. Further I can
 Able to process large data sets of structured and unstructured data of multiple GB files.
 Can able to create a Enterprise Data Warehouse.
 Can configure apache 2.4.1 and 2.6 clusters on a multimode environment.
 Visualize the data with the help of d3js for reporting.
 Can perform ETL operations on large data sets and apply machine learning algorithms like K-Means on the data.
 Create a Website using JSP and Servlets.
